Label: util_TNC Single - Cost
Expression: @(np.maximum(TNC_single_baseFare + df.s2_dist_skims * TNC_single_costPerMile + df.s2_time_skims * TNC_single_costPerMinute, TNC_single_baseFare) * 100 + df.s2_cost_skims) / (np.maximum(df.income,1000)**df.income_exponent)

Label: util_TNC Shared - Cost
